text: Aurangabad Central Vidhan Sabha constituency is one of the six constituencies of Maharashtra Vidhan Sabha located in Aurangabad district. It is a part of the Aurangabad (Lok Sabha constituency) along with five other assembly constituencies, viz Vaijapur, Gangapur, Aurangabad East, Kannad and Aurangabad West (SC) ==Members of Legislative Assembly== Key {| class="wikitable" |- !colspan="2"|Election!!Member!!Party |- |style="background-color: " | | 2009 | Pradeep Jaiswal | Independent |- |style="background-color: " | | 2014 | Imtiaz Jalil Sayed | All India Majlis-e-Ittehadul Muslimeen |- |style="background- color: " | |2019 |Pradeep Jaiswal |Shiv Sena |} ==Election results== ===Assembly Elections 2019=== ===Assembly Elections 2014=== ===Assembly Elections 2009=== ==References== Category:Aurangabad district, Maharashtra
